passiveSkills.name: Osmanthus's Boon
passiveSkills.desc: Chance to take 0 damage from an enemy attack.

advancedSkills.name: Aurous Storm Blade
advancedSkills.desc: Slash your surroundings with a powerful spinning attack. In EA mode, produce an osmanthus tornado around you that sweeps enemies up into the air.

advancedSkills.name: Spiral Thrust
advancedSkills.desc: Swiftly thrust ahead and send forth a spiral shockwave attack. In EA mode, the shockwave's range and number of hits increase.

advancedSkills.name: Calendula Cutter
advancedSkills.desc: Let rip a slashing attack from a quick-draw technique. Slashes deal Light damage and provoke any enemies hit. The slash flies further in EA mode.

advancedSkills.name: Light Ray Concentration
advancedSkills.desc: Fires a searing ray of concentrated light in a line directly ahead. Deals Light damage.

advancedSkills.name: Heavy Attack
advancedSkills.desc: Stronger than a Normal Attack. Use after a Normal Attack combo to branch into a Combo Finish. Hold the button for Bluewind Slash, a rising slash.
